{"tid":857310,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"SONY 官方正式宣布 PSN ID 更改功能即將推出！","createTime":"2018-10-11T04:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T14:10:50.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"49c81496728fd4c1ea0738522a1ac088c2fc6dfb","tid":857310,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"《PSN Online ID 更改功能》<br />\n<br />\nSony官方正式宣布PSN ID更改功能即將推出<br />\n現時容許個別獲選的 PlayStation Preview Program 用戶更改帳號名稱<br />\n預計明年年初會向所有 PS4 用戶公開<br />\nPSN ID更改功能將相容於2018年4月1日起發行的遊戲及絕大部分在這日期之前推出的PS4遊戲<br />\n但並非所有PS4、PS3、PSV與應用程式都保證支援這項功能<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/294753084191917/posts/741718959495325/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F294753084191917%2Fposts%2F741718959495325%2F&d=97fExk77nkGkdEDbKyWwYRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=39189af6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/294753084191917/posts/741718959495325/</a>"},{"pid":"8346c425d1a29070acc3aff8ff8025249fb1c09b","tid":857310,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/10/10/psn-name-change-preview/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2Fpsn-name-change-preview%2F&d=97fExk77nkGkdEDbKyWwYRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a830be1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/10/10/psn-name-change-preview/</a><br />\n<br />\n今天 PlayStation 方終於宣佈將會開始透過 PlayStation Preview Program 讓指定自願測試者修改 PSN ID 的服務，直至 11 月底為止。屆時大家將可透過系統設定或個人資料頁免費更換 PSN ID 一次，之後每次會收取 US$9.99；PlayStation Plus 會員則只需繳付 US$4.99。修改的時候，系統會讓你選擇要不要在你的新 ID 旁邊顯示你原本的 ID，讓你的朋友們還能容易辨認你。<br />\n<br />\n如無意外，該服務將會於 2019 初正式推出，到時候應該會有不少玩家考慮改名吧。要注意的是，PlayStation 說有一小部份相對老一點的遊戲可能會因沒法支持 PSN ID 的更改而產生問題；不過還好，如果你在公測期間遇到這種問題的話是可以免費還原你的 ID 一次。之後的安排就可能要視乎這次公測的表現了。"},{"pid":"daaecdaa5226f675ce33134564d2a71e3d643de1","tid":857310,"uid":32455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"嘩屌正啊，唔想再拎住個全名玩online<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5945c443db642fbea2cd439438e38a6e080c2581","tid":857310,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:41:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a27abf9aac9ee01a28445d05288ecc05c91397ec","tid":857310,"uid":115042,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"網上有單改粗口諧音俾Sony<br />\nban足8年，我諗最開心係佢"},{"pid":"187d2bc6a1901e3f45227ea49db1798fe31b63d8","tid":857310,"uid":90562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:30:13.000Z","msg":"德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a689680c63af59a57cf74d37a532bebcb2a0d953","tid":857310,"uid":57665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:32:54.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛買改名卡"},{"pid":"43afc9616362f22853ccbdc5e9675341b5e901f2","tid":857310,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"有樣野問, 當初係咪PSN 新起時,個底做得衰, 改名咁基本的野都搞咁耐先得?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS. 當初比佢昆左入真名,點知無得改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ... PSN 唔夠膽亂add  陌生人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7d8c81f4487aebb942574757035cde02dcb84a","tid":857310,"uid":49286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"表示等咗10年...."},{"pid":"81b45efea8740a89b1168733cff9f419e8285eac","tid":857310,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"終於可以用真名打機了"}]}